\b \cf0 Purpose\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf0 Our Program 7 is a java program that emulates the popular card game \'93Speed\'94. The user interacts with the program through a GUI designed to replicate what a typical game would look like. The difference is that, instead of sitting across from a human, the player is challenging an AI.\
